<%- headings = %w{RowID Sport Name Active Type Status MaxAge MinAge 
	              GenderType MaxPart MinPart MinMales MinFemales TeamSize 
	              Limit StartLimit } -%>
<%= headings.join(',') %>
<%= CSV.generate do |csv|
  @grades.each do |grade|
  	line = [ grade.database_rowid,
  		     grade.sport.name,
  		     grade.name,
  		     grade.active,
  		     grade.grade_type,
  		     grade.status,
  		     grade.max_age,
  		     grade.min_age,
  		     grade.gender_type,
  		     grade.max_participants,
  		     grade.min_participants,
  		     grade.min_males,
  		     grade.min_females,
  		     grade.team_size,
  		     grade.entry_limit,
  		     grade.starting_entry_limit ]
    csv << line
  end
end.html_safe %>

